System filesystems/partitions/LVs

Use LVs within the system VG

1. Use the same mechanism, replace /sbin/init with a script:

- during image creation: archive the content into a file
- during the boot:
- create LV
- create FS
- move the content from the rootfs to the new FS
- edit /etc/fstab


